        <div class="project">
            <h3>Project 2</h3>
            <p>Literature Review on Steganography

                Steganography, the art and science of concealing information within other data, has evolved significantly over the years. Early techniques focused on simple methods such as hiding text within other texts or images. However, recent advancements have expanded the field to include sophisticated algorithms and robust techniques for data concealment and extraction.</p>
